snippet.title: bhop pro: v1.5.8 - ios & android
snippet.description:
Android: https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.begma.bhoppro

iOS: https://itunes.apple.com/tr/app/bhop-pro/id1215690243

bhop pro v1.5.8 now available!

What's new?
mainmenu ui improvements
new map (speedrun: pillar)
new m9 bayonet skin (spitfire)
boost case added
ingame player death notifications added
map completion time added
case item showcase improved
rank up animation added
new mainmenu music

bhop pro ios and android gameplay.
